Detailed Description

EFI Time Abstraction: Year: 1998 - 20XX Month: 1 - 12 Day: 1 - 31 Hour: 0 - 23 Minute: 0 - 59 Second: 0 - 59 Nanosecond: 0 - 999,999,999 TimeZone: -1440 to 1440 or 2047
